PrecisAuthority (a) to enter into an AGREEMENT with the DISTRICT OF VANDERHOOF which provides for the transfer to the District of the lands, premises, equipment and chattels comprising and associated with VANDERHOOF AIRPORT at Vanderhoof, British Columbia, who undertakes to operate and maintain them as a licensed public airport, and (b) to accept the surrender of its current Lease (No. 112940) and another Lease held by the Vanderhoof Fall Fair Association (No. 90642).

precis:
Authority (a) to enter into an AGREEMENT with the DISTRICT OF VANDERHOOF
which provides for the transfer to the District of the lands, premises,
equipment and chattels comprising and associated with VANDERHOOF AIRPORT at
Vanderhoof, British Columbia, who undertakes to operate and maintain them
as a licensed public airport, and (b) to accept the surrender of its
current Lease (No. 112940) and another Lease held by the Vanderhoof Fall
Fair Association (No. 90642).
